text: Watertown is a city in the northeastern part of the U.S. state of South Dakota. It is the county seat of Codington County, and 22,655 people lived there at the 2020 census. Watertown became a city in 1885. == References == == Other websites == *City of Watertown website Category:County seats in South Dakota Category:Cities in South Dakota Category:1885 establishments in the United States Category:1880s establishments in Dakota Territory
